Choosing between Checkfront and Peek Pro in 2026 isn't just about features—it's about understanding how each platform scales with your operation. After evaluating both platforms across dozens of tour, activity, and rental businesses our team has consulted with, we've seen clear patterns emerge in where each excels and where each falls short.

The activity booking space has matured significantly, and both platforms have evolved. But the fundamental business model difference—subscription vs. commission—creates divergent incentives that affect everything from customer support responsiveness to feature development priorities.

